.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“让AI替人操作网页，安全必须是第一位的，”OpenAI在发布公告中反复强调。为避免AI越权或被恶意利用，ChatGPT Atlas为“智能体模式”设置了严格的技术边界。AI无法在浏览器中运行代码、下载文件或安装扩展，也不能访问电脑本地应用与文件系统；涉及银行、支付等敏感网站时，智能体会自动暂停并等待用户确认，防止非预期操作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">用户还拥有全程控制权，可通过界面按钮随时暂停、中断甚至接管AI操作；若担心数据安全，可选择“登出模式”（logged out mode）运行智能体。此时AI不会使用现有账号的Cookie，也不会自动登录任何平台。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过OpenAI也坦诚风险仍存。智能体可能在复杂任务中出错，且存在被网页隐藏的“恶意指令”诱导（即“间接提示注入”），可能导致数据窃取、执行错误操作。因此平台建议用户使用时尽量监控AI行为，敏感操作优先手动完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">04.个性化与隐私平衡：“浏览器记忆”可控可删</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"image-box\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"544077843\" data-ratio=\"0.5604166666666667\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 218.984px;width: 554.133px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.78552 / 1;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c1763b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIHiciaFjxeaJgVdNicfQibjTDicrriawXKFBPBibQENib8PXWJkNyQVqpbm7ZKUQbatI91SdIvYFzPTFrKw5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(102, 102, 102) !important;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(102, 102, 102) !important;font-weight:400;font-size:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">ChatGPT Atlas加入了可选的“浏览器记忆”功能</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为让AI更懂用户，ChatGPT Atlas加入了可选的“浏览器记忆”（Browser Memories）功能，同时通过多重设计保障数据隐私。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开启该功能后，ChatGPT会记录用户的浏览偏好、历史内容关键点，比如上周查看的招聘信息、收藏的装修案例，后续可直接提问“整理上周看的3个产品经理岗位要求”，AI会基于记忆快速生成总结。不过这些记忆仅归用户个人账号所有，默认不会用于OpenAI的模型训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;用户对“浏览器记忆”拥有完全控制权。在设置中可查看所有记忆内容，手动归档无用记录，或通过“清除浏览历史”键删除关联记忆；即使开启记忆，也能通过地址栏的“可见性开关”（Visibility Toggle），单独禁止ChatGPT读取某一网页内容，避免敏感信息被记录。此外，Atlas也支持隐身模式，开启后聊天记录、浏览历史均不会保存，AI也无法调用过往记忆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">05.macOS用户先行体验，Windows等版本正在开发中</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-exeditor-arbitrary-box=\"image-box\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"544077844\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 288.516px;width: 554.133px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.35518 / 1;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5cf2bef4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIHiciaFjxeaJgVdNicfQibjTDicrgsvhKWyqHHgmXdYZwPkib5HnTs99OLQFMuhVbuia4BF9rJ0Flfia73sFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(102, 102, 102) !important;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(102, 102, 102) !important;font-weight:400;font-size:14px !important;box-sizing:border-box;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">苹果Mac用户可六步完成ChatGPT Atlas的安装</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从发布当日起，全球ChatGPT用户可在chatgpt.com/atlas下载ChatGPT Atlas的macOS版本。ChatGPT的免费、Plus、Pro和Go用户均可免费使用基础浏览功能，比如AI搜索、侧边栏、光标聊天、浏览器记忆，但“智能体模式”仅限Plus、Pro、Business用户预览。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首次打开浏览器时，用户可一键导入现有浏览器（如Chrome、Safari）的书签、保存的密码和浏览历史，无需重新配置。OpenAI透露，Windows、iOS、Android版本已在开发中，具体上线时间将通过官方渠道通知。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Atlas的核心团队集结了多位浏览器领域资深人士，包括前Chrome工程师达林・费舍尔（Darin Fisher）、曾参与Chrome与Firefox开发的本・古杰尔（Ben Goodger），这被视为OpenAI保障产品兼容性与稳定性的重要布局。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">06.市场角逐：AI浏览器赛道升温，Atlas挑战与机遇并存</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT Atlas的发布，让本就火热的AI浏览器赛道竞争更趋激烈。目前市场上，Google Chrome以超60%的份额占据绝对主导，且正加速将Gemini AI深度嵌入浏览器，计划推出类似“智能体”的自动任务功能；微软Edge虽早一步整合Copilot，但市场份额不足6%，难以形成规模效应；AI搜索初创公司Perplexity此前推出的Comet浏览器，虽主打“AI问答+实时引用”，但在复杂任务执行能力上远不及Atlas的 “智能体模式”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对OpenAI而言，Atlas的优势在于ChatGPT超过8亿人的周活跃用户基础，这些用户对AI交互模式已有认知，转化门槛较低；但挑战同样明显，Chrome的用户习惯已根深蒂固，且依托谷歌搜索生态形成了强粘性，Atlas要撬动这部分用户，还需在功能稳定性、跨平台体验上持续优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">业内分析师认为，Atlas的意义不止于“一款新浏览器”，更标志着OpenAI向“AI互联网层”的布局。未来若越来越多用户通过AI智能体完成网页操作，广告、电商、服务推荐等互联网核心商业模式都可能重构。而互联网也将从“用户主动读写内容”的时代，逐步迈向“AI按意图执行任务”的“可执行”时代，ChatGPT Atlas正是这一转变的首个关键试验场。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 发布 AI 驱动的 ChatGPT Atlas 浏览器，以“智能体模式”和 AI 深度嵌入重构传统网页交互，挑战 Chrome 霸主地位。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 发布 AI 驱动的 ChatGPT Atlas 浏览器，以“智能体模式”和 AI 深度嵌入重构传统网页交互，挑战 Chrome 霸主地位。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 OpenAI 最新发布的 AI 驱动网页浏览器 ChatGPT Atlas。该产品旨在通过 AI 技术，将传统“点击链接找答案”的浏览模式转变为“意图驱动”的智能交互。其核心亮点是“智能体模式”，允许 AI 代表用户在网页上完成复杂任务，如自动购物和数据同步。此外，Atlas 还通过“搜索反转”直接提供 AI 整合答案、“上下文侧边栏”实现网页内容即时问答、“光标聊天”辅助文本编辑等功能，全面革新用户浏览体验。文章还强调了产品在安全和隐私方面的多重保障，包括对 AI 操作权限的严格限制和用户可控的“浏览器记忆”功能。目前 macOS 版本已上线，Windows、iOS、Android 版本正在开发中。文章最后分析了 ChatGPT Atlas 在激烈 AI 浏览器赛道中的机遇与挑战，并指出其发布标志着 OpenAI 向“AI 互联网层”的战略布局，预示着互联网商业模式和用户交互方式的深刻变革。",
